{"ts":"2026-06-05T04:44:50.008Z","author":"codex","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-todos-7l60"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Idempotent --upsert import (no duplicates on re-import)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Add an opt-in --upsert flag to 'pm todos import' that updates existing pm items instead of creating duplicates on re-import. Matches each incoming markdown checkbox to an existing item by (1) the embedded <!-- pm-id --> provenance comment the exporter emits, then (2) a stable title signature for hand-written files. Also parses the <!-- pm-id --> comment out of the title on every import so export->edit->import-with-upsert round-trips land edits on the same items. Default (no flag) behavior is unchanged: items are always created."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":[]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-06-05T04:44:50.008Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-05T04:44:50.008Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Default import still duplicates on re-run; --upsert keeps the item count stable and updates in place; export->import --upsert preserves ids and creates no duplicates; status not re-sent when unchanged; non-recursive bounded spawning; unit tests + functional test pass; changelog:check exits 0."}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"fbecd7f7ebb18ee95491231f069d46a9d4fabb090da1990a3eed8ec21fbe2aae","message":""}
